\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15731475 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2626886\charrsid3172719 Did you have to behave towards your brothers in certain ways?
