\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13449680 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2626886\charrsid3172719 No, never - I don't think so. No.
