\insrsid2626886\charrsid3172719  to consider certain things in life as very important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13449680 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2626886\charrsid3172719 Well - they did religiously like. No, I mean you've got to behave and - be - you understand.
