\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13449680 BS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2626886\charrsid3172719 Yes, I can. That was when I wasn
't very old and we lived - where I was born. I got a box of matches. And you know, they - thought it were very dangerous then you know. And I run outside - you know ours was a very big yard, all these six houses, and I ran outside with these and me dad af
ter me. And he caught me and I just said, bugger, like that. I don't know - and that was - oh I got a good belting for that you know. That's the only thing I can remember.
